      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Add</strong> the beef mixture to the pan&nbsp;and cook for 3 min or until starting to brown, breaking it up as you go</p>\r\n<p><strong>Meanwhile</strong>, chop the parsley roughly, including the stalks</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/634.-step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
