    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Once</strong> the rice is cooked, add it to the pan</p>\r\n<p><strong>Save</strong> a couple pinches of parsley for garnish and add the rest to the pan</p>\r\n<p><strong>Stir</strong> thoroughly&nbsp;to combine the flavours - this is your dirty rice</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
