    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Make</strong> 2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[4]</span> wells in the rice by pushing it aside (see picture)</p>\r\n<p><strong>Crack</strong> the eggs into the wells</p>\r\n<p><strong>Add</strong> a small splash of water to the pan</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cover</strong> and cook for 2-4 min or until the eggs are done to your liking</p>",
      "order": 7,
